w.esaim-proc.org/articles/proc/abs/2023/02/proc2307306/proc2307306.html&#34;&gt;Published&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;https://arxiv.org/abs/2207.12190&#34;&gt;Preprint&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/span&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- Meme chose mais en markdown. Pour l&#39;instant ne fonctionne pas avec les puces &#34;publication&#34; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- * Laurent Vidal, Tommaso Nottoli, Filippo Lipparini, &amp; Éric Cancès. **Geometric optimization of Restricted-Open and Complete Active Space Self-Consistent Field wavefunctions**. *The Journal of Physical Chemistry A (2024)* --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;br&gt;[Published](https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/acs.jpca.4c03213), [Preprint](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2404.14655) --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- * Éric Cancès, Muhammad Hassan, &amp; Laurent Vidal. **Modified-operator method for the --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- calculation of band diagrams of crystalline materials**. *Mathematics of Computation (2024)* --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;br&gt;[Published](https://www.ams.org/journals/mcom/2024-93-347/S0025-5718-2023-03897-2/), [Preprint](https://arxiv.org/pdf/2210.00442) --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- * Éric Cancès, Geneviève Dusson, Gaspard Kemlin &amp; Laurent Vidal. **On basis set optimisation in quantum chemistry**. *ESAIM: Proceedings and Surveys 73 (2023)* --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;br&gt;[Published](https://www.esaim-proc.org/articles/proc/abs/2023/02/proc2307306/proc2307306.html), [Preprint](https://arxiv.org/abs/2207.12190) --&gt;&#xA;&lt;br/&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- ## &lt;span style=&#39;font-family: Helvetica Neue;&#39;&gt; Preprints &lt;/span&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt;  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;ul class=&#34;pub-list&#34;&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!--   &lt;li&gt;Robert Benda, Éric Cancès, Emmanuel Giner &amp; Laurent Vidal. --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!--   &lt;strong&gt; Self-Consistent Field algorithms in Restricted Open-Shell Hartree-Fock &lt;/strong&gt;  --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!--   &lt;em&gt;Submitted (2024)&lt;/em&gt;. --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!--   &lt;br&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/preprint_ROHF.pdf&#34;&gt;Preprint&lt;/a&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!--   &lt;/li&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;/ul&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;/span&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;!-- &lt;br/&gt; --&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;span-stylefont-family-helvetica-neue-talks-span&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-family: Helvetica Neue;&#39;&gt; Talks &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;February – March 2023:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.siam.org/conferences-events/past-event-archive/cse23/&#34;&gt;SIAM CSE 23&lt;/a&gt; mini-symposium: Recent Advances in Numerical Methods for Electronic Structure Calculations. &amp;ldquo;Modified-Operator Method for the Calculation of Band Diagrams of Crystalline Materials&amp;rdquo; (&lt;a href=&#34;&#34;&gt;slides&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt;  &lt;strong&gt;August 2022&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://jahrestagung.gamm.org/annual-meeting-2022/annual-meeting/&#34;&gt;GAMM 92nd annual meeting&lt;/a&gt;, session 26 on Modelling, analysis and simulation of molecular systems. “On the approximation of energy bands in the Brillouin zone”. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;June 2021:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://erc-emc2.eu&#34;&gt;EMC2 meeting&lt;/a&gt;. “Methods for computing Restricted Open-Shell Hartree-Fock (ROHF) ground states”. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;br/&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;span-stylefont-family-helvetica-neue-other-conferences-and-workshops-span&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#39;font-family: Helvetica Neue;&#39;&gt; Other conferences and workshops &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;July 2025&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.cecam.org/workshop-details/advancing-simulation-analysis-and-prediction-of-complex-chemical-systems-using-modern-chemical-graph-theory-and-computational-topology-1389&#34;&gt;CECAM Workshop&lt;/a&gt; Advancing simulation, analysis and prediction of complex chemical systems using modern chemical graph theory and computational topology &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;August 2022&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;a href=&#34;https://school2022.dftk.org/&#34;&gt;DFTK school&lt;/a&gt; Numerical methods for density-functional theory simulations. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;June – July 2022:&lt;/strong&gt; International summer School in electronic structure Theory (&lt;a href=&#34;https://quantique.u-strasbg.fr/ISTPC/&#34;&gt;ISTPC&lt;/a&gt;). &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;June 2022:&lt;/strong&gt; GDR NBODY &lt;a href=&#34;https://wiki.lct.jussieu.fr/gdrnbody/index.php/MINI-SCHOOL_2022&#34;&gt;4th mini-school&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;font-size: 1.25rem; font-family: AbhayaLibre-Regular;&#34;&gt; &lt;strong&gt;July-August 2021:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://smai.emath.fr/cemracs/cemracs21/&#34;&gt;CEMRACS&lt;/a&gt; Data Assimilation and Reduced Modeling for High Dimensional Problems. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
